Grandia II [Single Disc] (NTSC-U) *Repack*
------------------------------------------

The game was freezing on a cut-scene after you go back to Roan's city. It took a while but I found
out the problem. For some reason, the song that played on the cut-scene was freezing the game if
it was downsampled, but after I restored the original file everything worked again. It increased
only around 600kb on overburn, so I doubt you'll have any problems burning this. At least, I
hadn't.

I hope this is the final release, I can't work on this game anymore LOL.

Don't forget reading the original readme below, it has important information. If this repack is
the first download for you of my release, be sure to read the overburn information.

